  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] But then that-- then it all seemed to change very quickly, with-- with the arrival of the-- what I assumed-- not that I knew what the hell was going on in the rest of the world, but I assumed that it was the Germans had then walked into-- into-- had occupied Hungary.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I remember this day being taken to the-- to this place and my pants being pulled down.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then my-- it all seemed to sort of cave in again.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It seemed we were back to-- my father, again, was sort of stressed out and saying, well, we're going to be deported, he was saying, and we're going to go on this train again.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He said we'd have to go back on the train.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were going to take us back on the train.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I have this thing about trains.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Although I always often wanted to go on a long train trip.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I don't like going on trains.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were supposed to go back on the train, somewhere.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Going back to-- to Poland.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think that what happened was that all the-- if there were-- if you were discovered, then you were then shipped, not back to the ghetto, but this time back-- this time to the concentration camp, Auschwitz or something.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Did you know about the concentration camps?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we knew because this is-- when we were in the ghetto, we knew the next step was going to a place where you never came back from.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, I knew there was-- this place existed.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
